These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, rock-climbing, card-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, volleyball, golf
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is sailing##2
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
4. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | card-games  | hiking | rock-climbing | puzzles  |
| Sport   | handball | volleyball   | golf  | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, cherry, orange, apple
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, accountant, teacher, photographer
1. the photographer is not to the left of the photographer##8
2. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
3. the person eating pumpkin is the accountant##1
4. the person eating apple is between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating cherry##2
5. the person eating cherry is somewhere between the person eating orange and the musician##7
6. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the person eating cherry##5
7. the musician is not to the left of the musician##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | orange | cherry          | apple | pumpkin     |
| Job    | teacher      | photographer | musician | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, musician, designer, doctor
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, documentary, musical
1. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the designer##8
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
3. the musician is on the right of the teacher##1
4. the musician is in an even position##4
5. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
6. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
7. the doctor is the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | teacher | musician | designer     | doctor |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | musical   | fantasy | documentary    |

