.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, house, hip-hop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rowing, rugby, swimming
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##8
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
7. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | house   | gospel         | hip-hop   | d&b    |
| Sport         | rowing | swimming | rugby | baseball |

