.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, sports, thriller, musical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, rowing, skateboarding
1. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person watching sports movies##7
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching spy movies##7
4. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person watching sports movies and the person who's sport is skiing##7
6. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | thriller | musical | spy    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | skateboarding   | rowing   | skiing |

