4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
5. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
6. the person eating mango is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
7. the person eating mango is the fan of gospel##1

