.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, milk, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, climbing, baseball, tennis
1. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's sport is baseball##7
3. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
4. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
5. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | milk | lemonade | coffee   |
| Sport      | basketball | baseball | tennis  | climbing |

