3. the nurse is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the nurse##7
5. the coach is not to the right of the software-developer##8
6. the software-developer is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the coach##7

.:: Answer ::.
