.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, house, trance, funk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, skateboard, airplane
1. the fan of rock is between the fan of funk and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
4. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the fan of trance is not the person driving the skateboard##6
7. the fan of funk is not to the right of the fan of trance##8
8. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | rock | trance | house |
| Transport     | airplane | jet-ski       | bike  | skateboard    |

