2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person eating zucchini##8
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating watermelon is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
6. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
7. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | zucchini        | grapes | watermelon      | cranberry    |
| Hobby   | video-games | dancing   | card-games | sudoku |

