The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, hiking, rock-climbing, camping
1. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
2. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
4. the person drinking water is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | water | coffee        | iced-tea       |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | hiking  | baking | camping |

