.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, asparagus, apple, plum
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, epic, musical
 1. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 2. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
 3. the person eating cucumber is the person watching epic movies##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is not to the right of the person watching mystery movies##8
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the person watching epic movies##8
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person eating cucumber##8
10. the person eating asparagus is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | asparagus    | apple | cucumber | plum |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | musical  | epic     | mystery    |

