.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, kiwi, apricot
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, woodworking, gardening
1. the person eating kiwi is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person eating kiwi is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person eating apricot##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person eating apricot##2
7. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | apricot        | cranberry | cherry | kiwi |
| Hobby   | gardening | woodworking | hiking   | fishing    |

