.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog, rat, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller, train, ship
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not the person driving the train##6
2. the person driving the train is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
3. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
6. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
7. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | hedgehog  | guinea-pig | frog  | rat  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | roller   | ship | train |

