.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goldfish, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, tram, airplane, quad-bike
1. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the bird##6
2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the train##1
5. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the train##7
6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
7. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the quad-bike and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | cat    | rat | bird | goldfish |
| Transport   | tram | quad-bike      | airplane     | train     |

 